00:01:59.000 --> 00:02:01.176
only 17 million people live there.

00:02:01.200 --> 00:02:05.960
We are short 125,000 nurses
over the coming years.

00:02:07.920 --> 00:02:09.656
But how did we even end up here,

00:02:09.680 --> 00:02:12.496
in this idea of placing
all kinds of sick people

00:02:12.520 --> 00:02:14.200
together in one big building?

00:02:15.680 --> 00:02:18.400
Well, we have to go back
to the Ancient Greeks.

00:02:19.200 --> 00:02:22.336
